{"parentUuid":"4abee174-5056-4c36-8665-964a8818b299","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"D:\\yyc\\claude","sessionId":"96426d6d-2dc8-451c-887b-a1b2a741c39d","version":"2.1.55","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"id":"msg_2026022609354820a8a5ddee794efb","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"glm-4.7","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Claude Code Help\n\nClaude Code is an AI-powered CLI assistant for software engineering tasks. Here's what you can do:\n\n## Common Commands\n\n| Command | Description |\n|---------|-------------|\n| `/help` | Show this help message |\n| `/clear` | Clear conversation history |\n| `/fast` | Toggle fast mode (faster output, same Opus 4.6 model) |\n| `/commit` | Create a git commit with staged changes |\n| `/tasks` | List all tasks in the task list |\n\n## Things I Can Help With\n\n- **Code editing**: Read, modify, create files\n- **Bug fixing**: Debug and resolve issues\n- **Code exploration**: Search and understand codebases\n- **Git operations**: Commits, branches, pull requests\n- **Testing**: Run tests, fix failures\n- **Refactoring**: Improve code structure\n- **Documentation**: Explain code and concepts\n\n## Available Skills\n\n- `ai-news-collector` - Collect AI news and updates\n- `gemini-image-generator` - Generate images with Gemini API\n- `notebooklm` - Query Google NotebookLM notebooks\n- `remotion-skills` - Create videos with Remotion\n- `skill-creator` - Create custom skills\n\n## Tips\n\n- Be specific about what you want to accomplish\n- I can work with multiple files in parallel\n- Ask for clarification if anything is unclear\n\nWhat would you like help with today?"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":23,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":17792,"output_tokens":339,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","ite